# Background
DeSoScams Team has been working diligently over the past couple of years trying to make DeSo a safer place for all its users. As a step towards making the DeSo experience a better one and also because scammers have started using bots and programming to scale their scams to the next level, we are looking to ramp up our efforts by building DeSoGuard to help users guard against scams, rug-pulls, bots and ghost-taggers. 

# Key Features
## Scam Account Identification
DeSoGuard utilizes advanced AI algorithms to identify accounts displaying characteristics commonly associated with scams including but not limited to money transactions with known scams. By identifying and flagging these potential scams, DeSo Guard plays a crucial role in ensuring a positive and secure experience for all users, especially newcomers who may not be fully aware of the prevalence of scams on the DeSo platform. 
## User Profile & History
DeSoGuard introduces a feature designed to enhance transparency and trustworthiness in the DeSo community. This feature displays a summary of a user's historical transactions, providing valuable insights into their behaviour and activity patterns on the platform.
## Rugs Identifier
Identify Accounts that have sold their own Creator Coins one or more times. While selling your own Creator Coin may still be acceptable  (especially if done with a warning to your investors), it is something that a few investors may not be comfortable with.
## Mass-Tags and Ghost Tags
Identify accounts that have a tendency to mass-tag 100s of users in their posts in order to get engagement. While some users may still do it with the permission of users that they tag, it is still a very annoying part of the user experience on DeSo.
## Bot Checker
DeSoGuard meticulously analyses user activities to identify accounts exhibiting bot-like behaviours, such as mass following and auto-liking all posts. These automated actions can be disruptive and annoying, detracting from the genuine human interactions that form the core of a rewarding social experience.
## AI Content Identification
DeSoGuard employs a sophisticated AI content detection system to scrutinize user posts and comments. By detecting AI-generated content, DeSo Guard effectively prevents these bad actors from gaining undue clout or influence under false pretences, ensuring a more authentic and trustable social media environment.
## Feedback & Continuous Improvement
DeSo Guard utilizes a community-driven feedback system where users can report false positives (legitimate activities flagged as suspicious) and false negatives (suspicious activities not flagged). This feature allows DeSo Guard to continuously learn and improve its accuracy, making the tool more adaptive and reliable based on real-world user experiences and inputs.
# Tokenomics
## Initial Round
We are looking to raise $10,000 to cover the costs of building an initial proof of concept and covering a year of website hosting and server costs, API costs and other incidentals along with development and marketing costs. We would of course welcome a larger amount and that would only push us to accelerate some of the features we have in our pipeline. 
## Token Usage
The Tokens will be used on Desoscams.com in various ways:
- Scam Check: To check if an account is a scam, one DSC Token will be used
- Governance: When Prioritizing key features, we'll look to our community to help us prioritize features
- Early Access: Our Top Token Holders will be given early access to the tool and possibly new features (in the future) as a perk & to ensure our tools are released to the general public after a round of QA.
- Priority Communication: Certain Exclusive Channels will be opened for those holding over 10K Tokens (100$ worth at launch price) and 50K Tokens (500$ at launch price).
- Exclusive Features: Certain Features involve significant API cost and we might need to restrict that to a limited number of users. We will set appropriate limits at an appropriate time in the future.

You are probably here because you want the DAO to do something. The primary mechanism by which the DAO gets things done is via "Requests for Proposal" (RFPs). An RFP is a request from the DAO for contributors to offer to do work on its behalf, and receive compensation in return.
Anyone who identifies a need can write an RFP, and if the RFP is passed, a proposal can be written in response and be awarded the work. Even if you believe you can do the work yourself, you will still need to pass an RFP in order to be awarded the work (and corresponding compensation) by the DAO.
RFPs vary in detail and complexity. An RFP for improving the DAO's documentation may only be a paragraph or two long, and proposals for it will be equally short. At the other extreme, an RFP for managing the DAO's funds may be lengthy, and a successful proposal could be multiple pages justifying the proposer's ability to take on the job.

# Vision - concept and broader objectives

Setu is built to make the userâ€™s life simple. We help leverage the best that web3 has to offer without you having to go through the dirty details. Using Setu is as simple as signing up and giving us permission to manage your presence across social media platforms. 

Setu builds automations between disconnected pieces of social media. This helps make social media more composable and manageable through a single window solution like Setu. Our deeper objective is to reduce friction for creators.


# Product Need

Newer monetisation channels such as social tokens, NFTs, tipping have immense potential. Yet users in general and creators in particular remain fixated on corporate social media. This could be due to two reasons: 

1. Network debt - users have a network already well developed which is hard to move 
2. Content debt - users have a huge backlog of content that they have created over the years 


# Objectives

1. Our first challenge is to make social media posts portable from corporate social media. All of this content is legally â€œownedâ€ by these platforms. While it is the creators whose blood, sweat and tears have gone into making this content. The ownership must be that of the creators. 

- Corporate social media is designed in a way to not allow users to own their own content. Or at least they do a good job of making it confusing. For creators to own their content, it must be stored in a decentralized database. Setu allows creators to make backups of their entire content library on blockchain. This has dual benefits as it also enriches the decentralised social media ecosystem with proven viral content. 

2. The next challenge is to move the community. Currently all of our social graphs live on corporate platforms. For decentralized social media to be successful, we must incentivise the social graph to move as well. This is how we solve network debt. 

3. Multiply Surface Area - Twitter does 280 letter messages. Medium does long form blog posts. YouTube does 9:16 video. TikTok does 16:9 video. Facebook does everything. A creator must also do everything, or at least have other people/tools supporting them that do this. 

- With the advances in machine learning, it is now possible to repurpose content from one channel to another. Imagine shooting 1 hour episode of a podcast and automatically generating 20 tiktoks, 100 tweets, 3 blog posts and all the other good stuff. Pretty cool? We know.  


# How do we make money? 

Our monetisation strategy is also based on the deeper vision of reducing friction for creators. We charge a small subscription fee if you choose to use any of our real time automations. 

If you choose to use the option to move all your content in one shot, then we charge on a per transaction basis.  


# Supporting the DeSo Movement

Setuâ€™s success is inextricably linked to the success of the DeSo protocol. Therefore we are investing heavily into positive sum actions for the whole ecosystem. 

We want to make it easy for people to understand and use decentralized social media. To that effect, we have created several explainer blogs, twitter threads.

Setu has also invested heavily into incentivizing people to use the DeSo protocol. We have run several giveaways to reward people who post on the platform. 

Ultimately Setu helps the entire DeSo ecosystem in 3 ways:   
1. Reduces friction for content creators to move into DeSo ðŸ¤  
2. Imports proven viral content into the blockchain increasing engagement ðŸ“ˆ  
3. Makes the benefits of DeSo more approachable to creators ðŸ’²

BlockGameX is about shifting and growing the economic power in gaming industry to content creators and gamers. 

Today, neither game content (Game Assets) creators ("Creators") nor game players ("Gamers") benefit from the popularity of a successful game. Creators merely get one time fee and players have no incentive to play other than the good old joy factor.

Independent Creators and Indie Studios working for big publishers have no control over the economic benefits arising out of the mass adoption of their gaming content. 

Gamers have no intrinsic benefit other than good old fun factor to play games. Play to earn games do not solve the problem as they are not building as sustainable economy. Gamers still can't call gaming a career. 

Only big publishers and gaming companies benefit out of the current industry setup. 

With BlockGameX, this is set to change where each use and each trade of game asset will reward the original Creator. Gamers will earn in real currency, i.e. cross Game Assets. Their career will not start every time a new game is launched. Instead, it will thrive from one game to another. Communities will be build around asset classes. Gamers will be able to monetize these communities using DeSo apps. 

The whole system will promote a web of connected games that will share Game Assets and communities. Overall the gaming industry will thrive in unison!

Creators will create and publish game assets to BlockGameX marketplace as NFT Master Classes. These game assets can be of any type like 3D model, a SFX collection, a VFX, or a complete 3D Game Asset with media and conformant API, etc. These NFT assets will have configurable economic parameters like maximum number of licenses, creatorâ€™s rate of return, etc. These parameters will help Creators build economic models around their products.

The more the asset will be used, the more will be the earnings for the Creator. The Creators will need to be competitive to survive in a demand driven economy.

Studios will buy NFT Master Class production license to include the assets in game and to mint NFT instances ("Instance") for use in game and for distribution as collectibles. Buying license for a NFT Master Class Game Asset will allow studios to enable gamers to use their "Owned Game Asset" ("OGA"), belonging to same NFT Master Class to be used in their game. This will encourage an ecosystem of games that allow asset sharing. This will solve the problem of Cold Start for newly launched games by bring in early adopters belonging to NFT Master Class community. These Instances can further be distributed by studios as in-game play rewards or as off-game as collectables. Gamers will earn and collect the Instances. They will be able to trade the Instances in open marketplaces. Each trade will pass back commission to the BlockGameX DAO shareholders, the minter Studio and the original Creator. Gamers will also have the option to burn the Instance to release the underlying asset.

So, get ready for the revolution in Gaming. All the power to the Creators and the Gamers!

# EchoDeSo Alliance DAO Project Proposal

## TL;DR Summary
EchoDeSo Alliance DAO is dedicated to elevating the DeSo Platform's visibility through diverse, high-quality content. With a $500 initial funding target, we aim to establish a solid online presence and incentivize content creation.

## Table of Contents

9. [Next Steps and Timeline](#9-next-steps-and-timeline)

## 1. Introduction
EchoDeSo Alliance DAO focuses on promoting the DeSo Platform through strategic content creation, aiming to create a dynamic and engaging digital narrative.

## 2. Project Goals and Objectives
Our objectives include:
- Producing authentic, high-quality content about DeSo.
- Encouraging a wide range of creators to contribute their unique perspectives.
- Ensuring variety in content, even on similar topics, to keep the conversation fresh.

## 3. How it Works
### Becoming a DAO Token Holder
- Purchase DAO Tokens at $0.01 each.
- Collaborate and make decisions in a private Telegram group.
- Voting occurs on the DeSo Platform, with influence proportional to your token holdings.
- At the close of every round, 10% of the funds raised are used to purchase $EchoDeSo Creator Coin and are then distributed across ALL DAO Token Holders who have been active for the last seven days.

### Investing in Creator Coin
- The $EchoDeSo Creator Coin is vital for the project's economy.
- The 20% Founders Reward, along with tips and earned $DESO, are reinvested into the Creator Coin, enhancing its value.

### Joining as a Content Creator
- Apply by submitting your bio and social media handles.
- Review available Topic bounties and request to create content for chosen topics.
- Once approved and upon successful submission, receive your bounty via the $EchoDeSo Creator Coin.

## 4. First Round Funding Goals
- **Domain Purchase:** Buy echodeso.com for $16 for a simple landing page.
- **Creator Coin Investment:** Start with a $100 investment in $EchoDeSo Creator Coin.
- **Administrative Setup:** Develop a landing page, online form designs, and content creation templates.

## 5. Structure and Governance
- Voting on the DeSo Platform determines DAO decisions.
- Your voting power is based on the number of DAO Tokens you hold, ensuring fair representation.

## 6. Bounty System and Creator Validation
- Bounties are calculated based on content impact and creator influence.
- Creators are vetted based on their past work and potential to deliver quality content.

## 7. DAO Facilitator Role and Compensation
- John Jardin (@JohnJardin) serves as the initial DAO Facilitator, managing without DAO Tokens.
- John receives a 15% admin fee for bounties except for content he creates.

## 8. Participation and Incentives
- **DAO Tokens:** For decision-making and influencing the project's direction.
- **$EchoDeSo Creator Coin:** An investment opportunity with growth potential.
- **Referral Bonus:** A 5% bonus for referring new participants to the DAO.

## 9. Next Steps and Timeline
- Launch the fundraising round.
- Establish the online presence and set up the content creation framework.
- Begin the journey of content creation and community building.

# Welcome to DeSoOps Club

## Introduction

We invite you to join us at [DeSoOps.com](https://desoops.com), which we aim to develop into the leading management and utility portal for DeSo users. Our initiative is off to a great start with successful distributions of $DESO, Tokens, and Creator Coins to our active community members. Your support can help us elevate DeSoOps to new heights!

## Supporting the Focus App Launch

DeSoOps is aligning its upcoming features with the launch of the "Focus" app by the core DeSo team, scheduled for [11th November 2024](https://focus.xyz). Our enhancements aim to integrate seamlessly with Focus, turning DeSoOps into a vital tool for all DeSo users. This will include a minimal monthly subscription fee of $0.99 for advanced features.

### Upcoming Enhancements:
- **DeSo Account Integration:** Users will be able to register and edit their profiles directly through the DeSoOps portal.
- **Enhanced Notification System:** Mobile push notifications will inform users about private messages, and receipts of cryptocurrency, tokens, NFTs, and other important account activities.
- **DeSo Chat Compatibility:** Full compatibility with the [DeSo Chat Protocol](https://chat.deso.com) for uninterrupted communication within the DeSo network.
- **Comprehensive Wallet Dashboard:** A user-friendly dashboard to view all non-NFT assets such as crypto, tokens, and Creator Coins, reflecting accurate crypto and market values.
- **Customizable Alerts:** Users can customize their notification preferences to avoid unnecessary alerts, with an option to opt-out of mass-tagging and other disturbances.

![DeSoOps Road Map To Focus Launch](https://i.imgur.com/ZODoSyu.jpeg)

## Fundraising Details

To realize these features, we require a budget of $4000. We have successfully raised $1000 thus far and plan to initiate further fundraising rounds to secure the necessary funds.

## DeSoOps Club Explained

DeSoOps operates with DAO-like features but is primarily managed by @JohnJardin through Agilit-e. This structure allows us to maintain a focused direction while incorporating community feedback into our operations.

- **Token-based Input:** Token holders are encouraged to submit feature requests and enhancements directly to @DeSoOps for consideration in future updates.
- **Investment Opportunities:** Support the development and expansion of DeSoOps by purchasing tokens during our funding rounds on [OpenFund](https://openfund.com/d/DeSoOps) or trading via the [DeSo DEX](https://openfund.com/trade/DeSoOps). These tokens not only help fund development but also entitle holders to a share of the generated revenue.

### Revenue Model and Tokenomics
- **Revenue Sources:** DeSoOps generates revenue through transaction fees, diamond tipping, Creator Coin Founders Reward, HeroSwap commissions, and planned monthly subscriptions (coming soon).
- **Revenue Distribution:** 50% of the revenue supports Agilit-e operations, and 50% is distributed among DeSoOps token holders, proportional to their token ownership. Revenue is only distributed to token holders who own a minimum of 100 tokens.
- **Token Sale Dynamics:**
   - **Current Price:** $0.03 per token as of 15th October 2024.
   - **Referral Incentive:** Earn a 5% commission for referring new participants.
   - **Token Pricing Model:** The price per token will increase by 10% for every $2000 raised, rounded to the nearest hundredth. For example:
       - After raising the next $2000, the price will increase from $0.03 to $0.04.
       - After an additional $2000, the price will increase from $0.04 to $0.05.
       - After raising another $2000 from a starting price of $0.10, the price will increase to $0.11.
       - **Starting from $0.11, after the next $2000, the price will increase from $0.11 to $0.12 + 10% of $0.12 = $0.132, rounded up to $0.13.**
   - **Reserve Rate:** 0% reserve rate.
